### 2. ç¼–å†™ç¬¬ä¸€ä¸ªAPIæµ‹è¯•
```python
import pytest
from pytestifyx import TestCase

class TestAPI(TestCase):
    def test_get_user_info(self):
        response = self.api.get("/api/user/1")
        assert response.status_code == 200
        assert response.json()["id"] == 1
```

